description "Geonosian Warrior 

A flight-capable, 2-life dexterous gunner with a Sonic stun Blaster and electric spear.

^2Weaponry: 
- Melee
- Geonosian Static Pike (Staff/Purple Saber)
-- Saber Defense (1)
-- No Blaster Block
-- No Saber Training
-- Shocks on hit
-- 105% more KB
-- 61/75% less DMG
-- 200% special DMG mult
-- 25/6% less reach
-- 33% more radius
- Geonosian Sonic Blaster (Bowcaster 1)
-- Stuns on hit
-- 25% more FP DMG
-- 25% less velocity
-- Mag reload
-- Prim only
- Concussion Grenades (2)

^8Attributes:
- Reinforcement (1)
- Stamina (3)
- Dexterity (2)
- Healing (1)
- Fuel Regen (2)
- Assemble (2)

^3Abilities:
- Flight (Jetpack)
-- No overheating
- Dodge (2) ^3[CS1]
- Dex Roll ^3[CS2]"